title: Aberg leads Big 12 Championship - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Aberg leads Big 12 Championship - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: Texas Tech junior Ludvig Aberg owns the lead going into the final round of the 2022 Big 12 Men's Golf Championship at 5-under-par, while the No. 5 Red Raiders are in fourth and six back in the team standings at the Whispering Pines Golf Club.
